0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"因為一早吹晒雞去港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcb2728ebd1a3c49a0778585fa67d534f24483c","tid":1518934,"uid":156767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"封鐵就去機埸遊車河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d19b5823279bf7bf53f59fd9040e8d0d5da74d2","tid":1518934,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又話星期六會做埋星期日嗰份<br />\n星期六入機場唔係仲好咩</blockquote>你坐機鐵入到去時啲狗乜都凖備好啦</blockquote><br />\n其實港島都係，吹晒風唔俾去，如果仲去嘅話好危險<br />\n我估佢睇死大家改唔到照去架啫"},{"pid":"7ecbc05d0137b525fb2e4c43a66e09b81fe199bf","tid":1518934,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1</a><br />\n為了防止狗賊唔比搵律師，請各位義士發夢之前搵一個信得過既家人或者朋友交低一個時間，例如我今日去夢遊, 若果我在夜晚2200之前無報平安, 就等於出左事, 要搵律師。地點可能有少少麻煩, 要走幾轉先知, 但係都好過比人拉48個鐘。當然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fxz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg&h=b31178b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/hb6qnadvjkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fhb6qnadvjkj31.jpg&h=d5f45a58&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}